flowRoot.flowPara: Generates a sweep and then the echo of this sweep is evaluated to evaluate the whole system. More modern devices are beeing used in eg. docsis networks.
If you project this principle on wires/antennas that that have been placed below the skin and eg. a webcam as return channel you could maybe even portscan humans or hijack their telemetry
Today we expect that digital technologies are used, but the old things maybe still up and running
